snippet.title: 2XKO: Introducing Duo Play - /dev diary
snippet.description:
Watch the developer showmatch: https://youtu.be/F4a7UzySL9o

Executive producer Tom Cannon and game director Shaun Rivera showcase the duo play system and talk about the evolution of 2XKO, Riot’s 2D tag fighter.

More 2XKO videos: https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=5hugGCZon3I, https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=BbwmX-coQCM, https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=9zNqyHAP9zc

Featured music:
Daydream - Mélonade from Sessions: Star Guardian Taliyah
Focus on the Good - Juan Jose Alba Gomez
Piltover Bridge (2XKO) - Riot Games
Champion Select (2XKO) - Riot Games
